Interface CopyableValueContainer

    All Known Subinterfaces:

    public interface CopyableValueContainer

    Represents a ValueContainer that can be copied.

      Creates a clone copy of this CopyableValueContainer as a new CopyableValueContainer such that all the Values are safely duplicated to the new instance.

    • Method Detail

      • copy

        CopyableValueContainer copy()
        Creates a clone copy of this CopyableValueContainer as a new CopyableValueContainer such that all the Values are safely duplicated to the new instance. It is not guaranteed that the returning container is of the same type as this container.
        Returns:
        The new copy
